# Debriefs Directory

This directory stores retrospective summaries of work sessions.

## Format

```markdown
# DeBrief: [What Happened]

**Date:** YYYY-MM-DD
**Session:** session-id

## What We Did

## What Worked

## What Was Tricky

## Lessons Learned

## Related
- playbooks/*.md
```

## Naming Convention

```
YYYY-MM-DD-debrief-[topic].md
```

## See Also

- `playbooks/gamma-loop-playbook.md` — The gamma-loop pattern
- `playbooks/debriefs-playbook.md` — How to write effective debriefs
